{"tid":2041862,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"係時候發動公投","createTime":"2020-05-29T13:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T13:23:42.000Z","uid":69696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"369dc8a3b70ad6fb775cd7847b743610be42ecde","tid":2041862,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:17:53.000Z","msg":"依家需要向國際表態，表示香港人唔會屈服<br />\n公投係表示民意既最好方法之一<br />\n可就三項議題發動公投：<br />\n<br />\n1．是否支持國安法<br />\n2．是否支持雙著選<br />\n3．是否支持港獨<br />\n<br />\n以上既民意可以推動／改變各國既行動同部署<br />\n但執行上有困難，所以上知道<br />\n<br />\n以下係我以往有關新行動建議既post，有時間可參考下：<br />\n<br />\n我諗到個推廣同標準化廣東話既方法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fwrGtS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fwrGtS</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心/唔知可以做咩/無力感重既人，同我入黎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2004465\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2004465</a><br />\n<br />\n[拋磚] 未來推動運動既小小建議<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1811436\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1811436</a><br />\n<br />\n想同大家講講之後既運動發展<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429773\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429773</a>"},{"pid":"ed595aa7b23f081eb79edf493afdf19684d5a684","tid":2041862,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cca6a61fe7bb732ce41d8e20d694bdd2e18391f","tid":2041862,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}